Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:02.63,0:00:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Cornelius Fudge, the minister of magic!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:06.76,0:00:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I still don't believe you're back...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.20,0:00:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe this, Fudge:  Avada Kedavra!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.14,0:00:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! - A heart-attack...surely...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:26.79,0:00:28.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaaaah....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.45,0:00:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Yes! The ministry has fallen!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:32.66,0:00:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! Now you're the minister...\NNay the king of all magic!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.57,0:00:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Voldemort... Take me right here!\NRight now, right here on\Nthe ministers desk!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.07,0:00:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get ya!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.21,0:00:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get ya!...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.41,0:00:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, trixie!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.23,0:01:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.47,0:01:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You wanna try something new?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... some new...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.69,0:01:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Get on the desk!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:19.83,0:01:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now sit up - bitch...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.24,0:01:27.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, command me, my Lord.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.83,0:01:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah, mmmmh, that's nice...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.09,0:02:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do now?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.17,0:02:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything we want...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.76,0:02:05.29,Default,,0,0,0,,hang out mostly...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.83,0:02:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we could watch a movie...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,how's about  'She's all that'? I've\Nnever seen the beginning of it...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.79,0:02:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling okay, my Lord?!!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.41,0:02:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I am, Quirrell!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.42,0:02:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, that's the dozenths time\Nyou called me that!!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.09,0:02:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I ah...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you a squirrel!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I called you a squirrel.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.19,0:02:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No! You're thinking about peon\Nwe sent to Azkaban!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.14,0:02:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not a peon!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.74,0:02:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He's more a man then you'll ever be....
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.06,0:02:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't do this.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.41,0:02:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm going to be evil with all of you,\NI need to be evil with ALL of you!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.08,0:02:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Evil with all of me?...Wha...\Nwhat does that mean...?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.98,0:02:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm all right here...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.54,0:02:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No! There are pieces of you missing!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.75,0:02:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you talking about my horcruxes???
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.64,0:02:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause if it...If it weren't for those\NI wouldn't even be here right now...!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember dad
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.38,0:03:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and I can't remember mom
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.47,0:03:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,and aunts and uncle aren't\Nquite the same
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:21.71,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I had him and life seemed fair
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.02,0:03:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,yes, I had him he was here
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.67,0:03:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,to give me strength, show concern,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.66,0:03:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for nothing in return
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.62,0:03:42.12,Default,,0,0,0,,say hello, talk me through
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.56,0:03:45.95,Default,,0,0,0,,do the things that fathers should do.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.66,0:03:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.28,0:03:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.39,0:04:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is, he's gone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:04.41,0:04:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and he's hung me out to dry
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,the joy he said he felt, well,...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.45,0:04:11.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it was a lie
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.74,0:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,but when I had him my life was fine
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.99,0:04:23.41,Default,,0,0,0,,when I had him he was mine
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.75,0:04:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd share his thoughts, be a friend
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.69,0:04:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,stick with me until the end
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.57,0:04:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,watch a movie, roller-skate
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.37,0:04:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,fill the world with fear and hate
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.06,0:04:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.71,0:04:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.80,0:04:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I'm all alone
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.69,0:04:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you're gone for good
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.55,0:05:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,now I'm stuck right here wishing\NI understood
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.95,0:05:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me hope when my\Nspells weren't right
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.66,0:05:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You gave me someone to hold\Nevery night
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.13,0:05:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.33,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.99,0:05:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.91,0:05:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just missing you
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.08,0:05:44.43,Default,,0,0,0,,My dark Lord, news from Severus Snape!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.90,0:05:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumbledore's dead and the Dementors\Nhave control of the castle.
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.84,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hogwarts is yours, my dark Lord!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.32,0:05:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah! Excellent!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.48,0:05:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare my flying-machine!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.01,0:05:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like I'm going back to Hogwarts...!
